interventions.description:
On this study, four settings are going to be evaluated being that High Swing Assistance, Neutral Swing Assistance, High Swing Resistance and Max Trajectory Control. The following settings will be used in all three conditions:

* Sitting program - "Min lean";
* Standing program - "Auto lean";
* Step initiation program - "ProStep+",
* Training mode - "Off",
* SmartAssist option - "2Free";
* Stance support - "Low". The level of stance support and swing assistance will be set symmetrically for the affected and non-affected side.

Each patient is going to walk 7 min (or min 25 gait cycles) with every setting

